So I haven't really been actively sharing my shots in Framed, but I feel like it would be good to start. So I recently started looking into the works of quite a well know F1 photographer, Darren Heath. Was actually quite hard to find a suitable spot to pull this off, but I managed to get some trackside sponsor signage to help out.
